        <title>如何通过 hugo 和 github pages 搭建一个博客</title>
        <link>https://aruCUMA.github.io/p/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87-hugo-%E5%92%8C-github-pages-%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/</link>
